  "title": "Sketchup Drafter / Interior Design Drafter",
  "description": "<p>Working hours 8.30am to 5.30pm, six days work week. Sunday off.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>This is not a sales position.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Assist Lead Designer in completing design drawings and draw technical drawings for different renovation trades.</p>\n<p>Must be willing to learn and adapt.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Knowledge and experience in Sketchup is a must, and knowledge in CAD is beneficial.</p>\n<p>Minimum 2 years experience in Interior design or related field.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>If you have no related experience, we also welcome fresh graduates on a 1 year contract basis, but attitude must be right. Training will be provided.</p>",
